  <title>Getting Started With <app>GTG</app></title>

  <p>Welcome to <app>Getting Things GNOME!</app> (<app>GTG</app>).  In <app>GTG</app>, everything is a task: from building a bridge over the Pacific Ocean, to changing a light bulb, or organizing a party.</p>

